### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081/api
@token = <paste_token_here>

### Signup
POST {{baseUrl}}/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "pankaj231",
  "email": "pankaj1@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "pankaj@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Get Current User (protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Room
POST {{baseUrl}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "general"
}

### List All Rooms
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Room (with members)
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Join Room
POST {{baseUrl}}/rooms/1/join
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Leave Room
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/rooms/1/join
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Send Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/rooms/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello everyone!"
}

### Get Messages (latest 50)
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Messages (paginated — before message id 20, limit 20)
GET {{baseUrl}}/rooms/1/messages?limit=20&before=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### WebSocket Chat
# Connect via a WebSocket client to:
# ws://localhost:8081/api/rooms/1/ws?token={{token}}
# Send JSON:  { "content": "hello via ws" }
# Receive broadcast messages from all room members
